sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant SignInPage as SignIn Page UI
    participant LoginForm as LoginForm (react-hook-form + zod)
    participant AuthAPI as POST /api/auth/sign-in
    participant Crypto as bcrypt compare
    participant Token as JWT service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Prisma)
    participant Dashboard as /dashboard route

    Admin->>SignInPage: Open /sign-in
    SignInPage->>LoginForm: Render form and client validation rules
    Admin->>LoginForm: Enter email and password
    LoginForm->>LoginForm: Validate fields with zod schema

    alt Invalid form payload
        LoginForm-->>Admin: Show inline validation errors
    else Valid payload
        LoginForm->>AuthAPI: Submit credentials
        AuthAPI->>DB: Find user by email
        DB-->>AuthAPI: User record + passwordHash
        AuthAPI->>Crypto: Compare password vs hash

        alt Invalid credentials
            Crypto-->>AuthAPI: comparison=false
            AuthAPI-->>LoginForm: 401 Unauthorized
            LoginForm-->>Admin: Show invalid credential message
        else Valid credentials
            Crypto-->>AuthAPI: comparison=true
            AuthAPI->>Token: Create JWT access and refresh tokens
            Token-->>AuthAPI: Signed tokens
            AuthAPI-->>LoginForm: 200 OK + secure cookie/session
            LoginForm->>Dashboard: Navigate to /dashboard
            Dashboard-->>Admin: Show portal overview
        end
    end
